{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-009","title":"Sentence 09","sectionId":"sentences-001","sectionTitle":"Sentence 01-10","pageStart":70,"pageEnd":76,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":60,"duplicateEntryCount":1,"pages":[{"number":70,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 09"},{"type":"text","text":"Quails typically have short rounded wings that enable them to spring"},{"type":"text","text":"into full flight instantly when disturbed in their hiding places."},{"type":"text","text":"鹌鹑通常长有短而圆的翅膀，这一特点使它们可以在受到干扰"},{"type":"text","text":"时瞬间展翅起飞，飞离它们的躲藏地。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Quails typically have short rounded wings。句中that引"},{"type":"text","text":"导一个定语从句，修饰wings。该定语从句中又包含一个when引导的时"},{"type":"text","text":"间状语从句。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"quail /kweɪl/ n. 鹌鹑 vi. 胆怯；畏缩","headword":"quail"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 因为胆怯（quail）而发抖（quake）"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 quail at/before sb./sth. 胆怯于…"},{"type":"entry","text":"typically /ˈtɪpɪkli/ ad. 典型地，有代表性地","headword":"typically"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 来自type（n. 典型）"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 typical a. 典型的；有代表性的"},{"type":"entry","text":"enable /ɪˈneɪbl/ vt. 使（某人）能够做某事；使可能","headword":"enable"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 en（使…）+able（有能力的）→使（某人）能够做某事"},{"type":"note","text":"反义 disable vt. 使失去能力；使无资格"},{"type":"entry","text":"spring /sprɪŋ/ n. 泉；弹簧；春天；跳","headword":"spring"}]},{"number":71,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"vi. 跳跃；突然猛烈地移动"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 sp+ring（铃声）→泉水叮咚似铃声→泉"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 spring into 突然做某事"},{"type":"entry","text":"flight /flaɪt/ n. 航程；班机；飞行；逃避","headword":"flight"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 take flight 逃走"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 flightless a. 不能飞的"},{"type":"entry","text":"instantly /ˈɪnstəntli/ ad. 立即地；马上地","headword":"instantly"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 immediately n. 立刻，立即"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 instant a. 立即的；马上的 n. 立即；瞬间"},{"type":"