my 天敌"},{"type":"entry","text":"nestling /ˈnestlɪŋ/ n. 尚未离巢的小鸟","headword":"nestling"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 nestling feather 新羽"},{"type":"entry","text":"yearling /ˈjɪrlɪŋ/ n. 一岁的动物","headword":"yearling"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 来自year（n. 年；一年）"},{"type":"entry","text":"long-billed /ˈlɔːŋbɪl/ a. 长喙的","headword":"long-billed"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 long（长）+billed（喙的）→长喙的"}]},{"number":75,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"ornithology /ˌɔːrnɪˈθɑːlədʒi/ n. 鸟类学","headword":"ornithology"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 ornithologist n. 鸟类学家"},{"type":"entry","text":"plume /pluːm/ n. 羽毛，羽饰","headword":"plume"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 plumage n. 羽衣（鸟体的全部羽毛）"},{"type":"entry","text":"preen gland [鸟]羽脂腺","headword":"preen gland"},{"type":"entry","text":"receptor /rɪˈseptər/ n. 接收器；感受器","headword":"receptor"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 re（表加强）+cept（拿，取）+or→用力拿住→感受器"},{"type":"entry","text":"seabird /ˈsiːbɜːrd/ n. 海鸟","headword":"seabird"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 sea（海）+bird（鸟）→海鸟"},{"type":"entry","text":"sensory /ˈsensəri/ a. 感觉的，感官的","headword":"sensory"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 sens（感觉）+ory→感觉的"},{"type":"entry","text":"wader /ˈweɪdər/ n. 涉水鸟，涉禽","headword":"wader"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 wade（跋涉）+r→涉禽"},{"type":"entry","text":"warbler /ˈwɔːrblər/ n. [鸟]刺嘴莺，鸣禽","headword":"warbler"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 warble v. 鸣叫"},{"type":"entry","text":"waterfowl /ˈwɔːtərfaʊl/ n. 水禽，水鸟","headword":"waterfowl"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 water（水）+fowl（飞禽）→水禽"},{"type":"entry","text":"courtship /ˈkɔːrtʃɪp/ n. 求爱；求婚","headword":"courtship"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 court n. 奉承；求爱 vt. 献殷勤；求爱"},{"type":"text","text":"displacement activity 替换行为"},{"type":"text","text":"distraction display 迷惑行为"},{"type":"entry","text":"fend /fend/ v. 照料；抵挡","headword":"fend"}]},{"number":76,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"同根 fender n. 挡板；栅栏"},{"type":"text","text":"food begging behavior 乞食行为"},{"type":"entry","text":"incubate /ˈɪŋkjubeɪt/ vt. 孵化；培育","headword":"incubate"},{"type":"note",